title: SwifTEA: New Music and Future Wins
description:
It's time to sneak in an episode because a lot has been going down in the Swiftie universe! Why did she pull Fearless (Taylor's Version) out of the Grammys and CMAs considerations? Is she really planning on releasing music with Adele? And why have we been so silent about Renegade up until now?
Lots of questions. Lots of answers. Let's discuss!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear? Let us know!
